1
00:01:37,900 --> 00:01:41,030
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:43,970
[Episode 11]

3
00:01:46,610 --> 00:01:48,120
How could it be the towels' fault?

4
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:50,039
Our hotel has been working with that

5
00:01:50,039 --> 00:01:52,140
towel brand and laundry for over 10 years.

6
00:01:52,140 --> 00:01:53,570
Never once has a guest

7
00:01:53,610 --> 00:01:54,990
had an allergic reaction.

8
00:01:54,990 --> 00:01:56,400
Then maybe the guest

9
00:01:56,430 --> 00:01:58,200
just has sensitive skin.

10
00:01:58,200 --> 00:01:58,789
So she-

11
00:01:58,789 --> 00:02:00,610
Then it's even less our problem.

12
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,070
She's the one with sensitive skin.

13
00:02:02,070 --> 00:02:03,670
What's that got to do with us?

14
00:02:03,670 --> 00:02:05,180
Trying to scam the hotel?

15
00:02:05,540 --> 00:02:07,800
Don't even bother with people like that.

16
00:02:08,590 --> 00:02:09,800
The guests in that room

17
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:12,170
are a few ladies
from a senior modeling team.

18
00:02:12,170 --> 00:02:14,030
They've stayed here for a long time.

19
00:02:14,030 --> 00:02:15,490
And they're quite easy to get along with.

20
00:02:15,490 --> 00:02:16,910
I really don't think they would-

21
00:02:16,910 --> 00:02:19,600
They stayed a long time, spent a lot,

22
00:02:19,620 --> 00:02:21,770
then right before checkout,

23
00:02:21,790 --> 00:02:23,360
find an excuse
to get their room comped.

24
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:25,400
Trying to pull a fast one on me?

25
00:02:25,400 --> 00:02:26,590
No way.

26
00:02:27,110 --> 00:02:28,040
Go reply to them.

27
00:02:28,070 --> 00:02:30,030
And be firm when you do.

28
00:02:30,079 --> 00:02:31,350
Tell them there's absolutely

29
00:02:31,350 --> 00:02:33,079
nothing wrong with our towels.

30
00:02:34,430 --> 00:02:36,310
Mr. Feng, shouldn't we

31
00:02:36,310 --> 00:02:37,870
check our towels first

32
00:02:37,870 --> 00:02:39,079
to make sure there's no problem?

33
00:02:39,079 --> 00:02:40,680
Check what?

34
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,560
Didn't I just tell you?

35
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:43,190
There's no problem with the hotel!

36
00:02:43,190 --> 00:02:45,110
Get this straight, Xu Miyu.

37
00:02:45,180 --> 00:02:46,800
You are a forewoman now.

38
00:02:46,800 --> 00:02:47,870
You need to see things

39
00:02:47,870 --> 00:02:49,560
from the hotel's perspective.

40
00:02:49,560 --> 00:02:51,420
Otherwise, what do I need you for?

41
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,680
But I think I...

42
00:02:55,790 --> 00:02:56,980
Why are you still standing here?

43
00:02:56,980 --> 00:02:57,980
Get to work!

44
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,400
You're just so dense!

45
00:03:01,960 --> 00:03:03,030
Hello?

46
00:03:03,510 --> 00:03:05,140
Yes, it's me.

47
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,280
Yes.

48
00:03:08,140 --> 00:03:09,140
Okay.

49
00:03:37,030 --> 00:03:40,079
Hello, is this Xingkang Testing Center?

50
00:03:40,079 --> 00:03:42,030
Yes. How can I help you?

51
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:44,590
I have some towels and sheets here.

52
00:03:44,590 --> 00:03:46,680
I'd like to get them tested

53
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,010
for detergent residue.

54
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,800
We're really sorry.

55
00:03:50,240 --> 00:03:51,470
The hotel will definitely

56
00:03:51,470 --> 00:03:52,960
look into this.

57
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,680
Once we get the results,

58
00:03:54,680 --> 00:03:56,680
we'll give you a satisfactory answer.

59
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,520
When will the results come out?

60
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,880
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

61
00:03:59,900 --> 00:04:02,080
Don't try to drag this out.

62
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:04,560
Once this hits the news,

63
00:04:04,870 --> 00:04:07,310
your hotel will suffer the consequences.

64
00:04:07,310 --> 00:04:08,430
Don't play tricks.

65
00:04:09,370 --> 00:04:10,300
Go reply to them.

66
00:04:10,330 --> 00:04:12,240
And be firm when you do.

67
00:04:12,270 --> 00:04:13,610
Tell them there's absolutely

68
00:04:13,610 --> 00:04:15,340
nothing wrong with our towels.

69
00:04:16,329 --> 00:04:18,240
We won't. Rest assured.

70
00:04:18,269 --> 00:04:20,000
Our hotel isn't just any hotel.

71
00:04:20,019 --> 00:04:21,700
We will never brush it off.

72
00:04:21,950 --> 00:04:24,630
We just need some time

73
00:04:24,650 --> 00:04:26,380
to find the root of the problem.

74
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:28,190
After all, nothing like this

75
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:29,650
has ever happened before.

76
00:04:30,250 --> 00:04:31,370
Guess I'm just unlucky.

77
00:04:31,370 --> 00:04:32,240
Let's go home.

78
00:04:32,790 --> 00:04:33,900
Fang.

79
00:04:33,950 --> 00:04:36,590
Ms. Xu, you're a nice person,

80
00:04:36,610 --> 00:04:38,610
and you've taken good care of us.

81
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:40,760
But you can't keep dodging

82
00:04:40,780 --> 00:04:42,100
the towel issue.

83
00:04:41,990 --> 00:04:47,770
[Recording]

84
00:04:42,310 --> 00:04:43,040
Yes.

85
00:04:43,060 --> 00:04:44,890
Fang was fine

86
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:46,450
before she used your towels

87
00:04:46,510 --> 00:04:48,000
as a pillow for a few days,

88
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:49,240
and ended up like this.

89
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:49,670
Yes.

90
00:04:49,700 --> 00:04:51,310
If it's not your hotel's responsibility,

91
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:52,630
what else is?

92
00:04:52,790 --> 00:04:53,720
I get it.

93
00:04:53,740 --> 00:04:54,940
Please rest assured.

94
00:04:55,090 --> 00:04:57,220
We will investigate this thoroughly.

95
00:04:57,510 --> 00:04:59,580
We're really sorry

96
00:04:59,640 --> 00:05:00,720
for the trouble.

97
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:05,820
[Recording]

98
00:05:01,390 --> 00:05:02,680
What good is sorry?

99
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:03,570
Exactly.

100
00:05:19,570 --> 00:05:21,010
Driver, follow that car.

101
00:05:34,020 --> 00:05:37,880
[Test Report]

102
00:05:39,690 --> 00:05:42,330
[Test Report]

103
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,830
Mr. Ji, how can I help you?

104
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,020
Take a look at this.

105
00:06:03,030 --> 00:06:04,920
[Test Report]

106
00:06:07,690 --> 00:06:08,580
[Test Report]

107
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,140
[Total bacteria count: Failed]
[E. coli: Failed]

108
00:06:10,730 --> 00:06:11,580
This is...

109
00:06:11,610 --> 00:06:13,940
The test results of the hotel bath towels.

110
00:06:14,510 --> 00:06:16,000
So our hotel towels

111
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:17,330
really are the problem.

112
00:06:17,360 --> 00:06:19,380
That's why the guest
had an allergic reaction.

113
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:20,580
I'll go find Mr. Feng.

114
00:06:20,880 --> 00:06:21,710
Miyu.

115
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:23,770
Take a look.

116
00:06:23,850 --> 00:06:25,120
You're in the video.

117
00:06:27,740 --> 00:06:29,480
Someone in the room
had an allergic reaction.

118
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:31,240
Her neck is all swollen.

119
00:06:32,620 --> 00:06:33,820
A towel allergy?

120
00:06:33,850 --> 00:06:34,600
You must give us

121
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,800
an explanation today.

122
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:37,600
Our hotel isn't just any hotel.

123
00:06:37,600 --> 00:06:39,720
Nothing like this
has ever happened before.

124
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,050
Guess I'm just unlucky.

125
00:06:45,800 --> 00:06:46,510
Ms. Xu.

126
00:06:46,510 --> 00:06:48,720
Rooms 1806 and 1817 are checking out.

127
00:06:49,250 --> 00:06:50,050
Got it.

128
00:06:50,470 --> 00:06:51,430
Go get Yin Xiang,

129
00:06:51,430 --> 00:06:52,600
and you two go clean up

130
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:54,040
Rooms 1806 and 1817 together.

131
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:55,159
She went back to the dorm.

132
00:06:55,159 --> 00:06:57,480
She forgot her phone and went to get it.

133
00:07:00,190 --> 00:07:02,250
What are you still standing here for?

134
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:04,560
Ms. Xu.

135
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:06,430
Rooms 1811 and 1816 are checking out.

136
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:07,120
Got it.

137
00:07:09,480 --> 00:07:10,630
The number of guests checking out

138
00:07:10,630 --> 00:07:11,760
will only increase.

139
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,170
You need to be prepared.

140
00:07:15,960 --> 00:07:16,730
Ke,

141
00:07:16,750 --> 00:07:19,210
go call Luo Qingping back
from her vacation.

142
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:26,280
Everyone, gather at the Linen Room now.

143
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:27,910
That won't work.

144
00:07:28,390 --> 00:07:29,560
No one replies

145
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:31,020
to mass messages.

146
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:33,409
You have to send
voice messages one by one.

147
00:07:35,060 --> 00:07:35,850
Stay calm.

148
00:07:36,090 --> 00:07:37,220
This is exactly when

149
00:07:37,220 --> 00:07:38,580
you can't act impulsively.

150
00:07:38,580 --> 00:07:39,460
Got it.

151
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,070
Let's get out of here quickly.

152
00:07:47,070 --> 00:07:48,680
I'm never coming back again.

153
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:57,480
Seriously.

154
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,600
What kind of hotel is this?

155
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,680
It's so disgusting!

156
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:01,830
Exactly. How can anyone stay here?

157
00:08:02,480 --> 00:08:03,480
I'm so mad!

158
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:09,210
I'll never stay here again!

159
00:08:09,710 --> 00:08:12,080
[Minhang Road]

160
00:08:18,730 --> 00:08:20,380
Hello everyone. My name is Peng Jie.

161
00:08:20,380 --> 00:08:23,270
I'm here to report serious hygiene issues

162
00:08:23,300 --> 00:08:25,030
with the linen at Purong Hotel.

163
00:08:25,230 --> 00:08:28,280
Last week, my team and I
stayed at Purong Hotel.

164
00:08:26,850 --> 00:08:30,040
[Name: Peng Jie]

165
00:08:28,520 --> 00:08:32,179
Our lead model unexpectedly
had an allergic reaction from the towels.

166
00:08:32,179 --> 00:08:33,610
This is my test report.

167
00:08:32,460 --> 00:08:34,450
[Test Report]

168
00:08:34,150 --> 00:08:36,240
The towels contain excessive bleach.

169
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:38,330
All three bacteria tests failed.

170
00:08:45,100 --> 00:08:47,200
The excessive bleach incident
at Purong Hotel

171
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,940
has drawn widespread attention today.

172
00:08:48,940 --> 00:08:49,920
According to reports,

173
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:52,510
a guest developed an allergic reaction

174
00:08:52,510 --> 00:08:53,790
after using hotel towels

175
00:08:53,790 --> 00:08:54,870
during their stay.

176
00:08:57,800 --> 00:09:00,140
A single spark
can start a fire these days, huh?

177
00:09:00,140 --> 00:09:01,230
It's just a towel.

178
00:09:01,260 --> 00:09:03,860
Is it necessary
to make such a big deal out of it?

179
00:09:10,070 --> 00:09:12,430
Go on! Move!

180
00:09:14,970 --> 00:09:16,800
Just shift over a little. Problem solved.

181
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:17,680
Psycho!

182
00:09:19,890 --> 00:09:20,880
[Wei Siyuan]
[Answer][Decline]

183
00:09:27,580 --> 00:09:28,910
Are you sober yet?

184
00:09:28,930 --> 00:09:30,200
Well, I...

185
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:31,360
I'm already on my way.

186
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:32,380
I'll be there soon.

187
00:09:32,380 --> 00:09:33,220
Um,

188
00:09:33,790 --> 00:09:35,240
let me handle this.

189
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:36,670
Mr. Wei,

190
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:38,870
I already have a solution.

191
00:09:39,030 --> 00:09:40,240
You better have.

192
00:09:41,420 --> 00:09:42,190
[Wei Siyuan
Call Ended]

193
00:10:04,710 --> 00:10:05,950
How many have you got?

194
00:10:05,970 --> 00:10:07,230
Five already.

195
00:10:07,370 --> 00:10:09,400
That whole row over there—all checked out.

196
00:10:09,400 --> 00:10:10,940
Same here.

197
00:10:11,250 --> 00:10:13,130
I heard the Laundry Room is full,

198
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:14,440
and the linen carts can't get through.

199
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,550
All stuck in traffic.

200
00:10:15,550 --> 00:10:16,600
-Really?
-At a time like this,

201
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,550
you two are still chatting?

202
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:18,150
Make way.

203
00:10:18,150 --> 00:10:19,720
Why? What's your problem?

204
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,670
We've been busy since early morning.

205
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:21,910
And we can't even say a word?

206
00:10:21,910 --> 00:10:23,340
It's not like I made the guests check out.

207
00:10:23,340 --> 00:10:25,100
Step back, Xiaoxue.

208
00:10:25,910 --> 00:10:27,240
Is no one in charge here?

209
00:10:28,060 --> 00:10:29,420
Sorry, my bad.

210
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,850
Sorry, my bad.

211
00:10:35,130 --> 00:10:36,380
Come on, this way.

212
00:10:36,870 --> 00:10:37,810
Sorry.

213
00:10:43,740 --> 00:10:44,670
Move forward.

214
00:10:48,510 --> 00:10:49,700
Miyu.

215
00:10:50,120 --> 00:10:51,780
Is there more after this load?

216
00:10:53,180 --> 00:10:54,360
I don't know either.

217
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:57,140
Room 1808 checking out.
Room 1807 checking out.

218
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:00,690
Got it.

219
00:11:00,710 --> 00:11:01,700
Alright.

220
00:11:01,790 --> 00:11:03,220
If anyone's gonna break down,
it's not you.

221
00:11:03,220 --> 00:11:04,350
Stop being so whiny.

222
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:06,880
I refunded my ticket home.

223
00:11:06,970 --> 00:11:08,920
And they charged a 20% cancellation fee.

224
00:11:08,920 --> 00:11:10,040
Then don't come.

225
00:11:10,060 --> 00:11:12,300
It's not like the executive floor
can't do without you.

226
00:11:12,300 --> 00:11:13,320
Go be a college student.

227
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,580
Enough. Stop arguing.

228
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:16,310
Move this cart out,

229
00:11:16,330 --> 00:11:18,740
then everyone head back
to the Linen Room to rest.

230
00:11:18,740 --> 00:11:19,540
Good work.

231
00:11:21,580 --> 00:11:22,680
Sorry

232
00:11:23,060 --> 00:11:25,190
to call you back while you're on leave.

233
00:11:26,350 --> 00:11:27,610
You already called me.

234
00:11:27,690 --> 00:11:29,050
Save the sweet talk.

235
00:11:31,120 --> 00:11:33,710
Well, when I came up just now,

236
00:11:33,730 --> 00:11:35,950
I saw that the other floors
were a total mess.

237
00:11:35,950 --> 00:11:38,550
Ours is at least... somewhat organized.

238
00:11:49,910 --> 00:11:51,710
You guys are taking a break here?

239
00:11:52,390 --> 00:11:55,240
There's been a lot of drama
on your executive floor lately.

240
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:57,510
First, Black Card Ji came

241
00:11:57,510 --> 00:11:59,320
and terrified everyone.

242
00:11:59,340 --> 00:12:00,320
Then right after that,

243
00:12:00,320 --> 00:12:01,910
Mr. Duan Jr. arrived

244
00:12:01,910 --> 00:12:03,170
in all his glory,

245
00:12:03,210 --> 00:12:05,800
clearing out
he executive floor in a flash.

246
00:12:05,820 --> 00:12:06,940
And now look,

247
00:12:06,970 --> 00:12:09,300
the whole hotel is having a mass checkout.

248
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,630
All of us other departments

249
00:12:10,630 --> 00:12:12,630
are stuck cleaning up your mess.

250
00:12:12,660 --> 00:12:13,570
Such bad luck.

251
00:12:13,840 --> 00:12:15,910
Well, Xiaoyan,
you can't blame me for that.

252
00:12:15,910 --> 00:12:17,320
I'm exhausted too.

253
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,320
Look at me,

254
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,270
my hands are swollen.

255
00:12:21,610 --> 00:12:23,450
Look at my legs, will you?

256
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:26,470
I've been standing all morning.
They're like two logs by now.

257
00:12:26,470 --> 00:12:28,940
The bell desk is also complaining.

258
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,320
You executive floor staff

259
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,790
better keep a low profile now,

260
00:12:31,790 --> 00:12:33,320
or you might get jumped.

261
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:35,910
I actually wish
someone would knock me out,

262
00:12:36,150 --> 00:12:37,630
so I could comfortably

263
00:12:37,630 --> 00:12:39,200
rest in the dorm.

264
00:12:39,230 --> 00:12:40,320
You have no idea—

265
00:12:40,320 --> 00:12:42,440
the executive floor
is covered in linens now.

266
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,360
It's a nightmare.

267
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:44,760
I don't even dare to go up.

268
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:46,950
Ke? Ke, are you there?

269
00:12:46,970 --> 00:12:48,370
Please reply if you copy.

270
00:12:48,570 --> 00:12:49,650
They're calling you.

271
00:12:49,650 --> 00:12:51,010
Hurry up and get to work.

272
00:12:53,530 --> 00:12:55,750
It's fine. I'll just pretend
I didn't get it.

273
00:12:55,750 --> 00:12:56,910
I'll hang out with you guys a bit longer.

274
00:12:56,910 --> 00:12:58,630
Aren't you afraid
your forewoman will yell at you?

275
00:12:58,630 --> 00:13:00,320
Miyu wouldn't do that.

276
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:01,340
We just give her

277
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:02,870
all the work we don't want to do,

278
00:13:02,870 --> 00:13:04,130
and she'll do it for us.

279
00:13:04,210 --> 00:13:06,540
Your forewoman's that much of a pushover?

280
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:07,790
Of course.

281
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:10,010
She didn't earn her position.

282
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:11,640
So what right does she have to manage you?

283
00:13:11,640 --> 00:13:12,470
True.

284
00:13:31,700 --> 00:13:32,470
Ms. Xu,

285
00:13:32,510 --> 00:13:34,370
the new laundry's
finished linens are here.

286
00:13:34,370 --> 00:13:36,720
Mr. Feng wants them replaced immediately.

287
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:37,550
Got it.

288
00:13:38,650 --> 00:13:39,250
Four.

289
00:13:40,420 --> 00:13:42,290
Everyone, the new linens are here.

290
00:13:42,290 --> 00:13:44,620
Please do another round of replacements.

291
00:14:24,290 --> 00:14:25,770
Here, let me help you.

292
00:14:25,820 --> 00:14:26,640
Thank you.

293
00:14:26,670 --> 00:14:27,570
Careful.

294
00:14:27,670 --> 00:14:28,190
Okay.

295
00:14:28,240 --> 00:14:28,890
Okay.

296
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:30,080
Sir,

297
00:14:30,150 --> 00:14:31,510
how did you get in here?

298
00:14:31,530 --> 00:14:33,800
This is the Laundry Room,
a major work area.

299
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,460
Outsiders are not allowed in.

300
00:14:35,460 --> 00:14:36,190
I'm sorry.

301
00:14:36,290 --> 00:14:37,440
I just want to wash some clothes.

302
00:14:37,440 --> 00:14:38,280
I'm in a hurry to wear them.

303
00:14:38,280 --> 00:14:39,810
Can you do me a favor?

304
00:14:39,940 --> 00:14:40,750
No, no.

305
00:14:40,750 --> 00:14:42,600
You have to follow the process.

306
00:14:42,600 --> 00:14:44,460
Register at the HSKP Department first.

307
00:14:44,460 --> 00:14:45,790
I know the process.

308
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:47,670
I've worked at Purong Hotel for years.

309
00:14:47,670 --> 00:14:48,850
I'm a veteran employee.

310
00:14:48,850 --> 00:14:50,290
Doesn't matter if you're a veteran.

311
00:14:50,290 --> 00:14:51,750
Our linens haven't even been

312
00:14:51,750 --> 00:14:52,910
sent out to wash yet.

313
00:14:52,910 --> 00:14:54,880
They've been piling up for half a day.

314
00:14:54,880 --> 00:14:57,510
I remember this place
used to be quite efficient.

315
00:14:57,510 --> 00:15:00,090
Why are there so many piling up now?

316
00:15:00,720 --> 00:15:01,670
You know how it was.

317
00:15:01,670 --> 00:15:04,000
Everything used to be well-organized.

318
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:04,720
But now,

319
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:06,500
it's a mess everywhere.

320
00:15:06,530 --> 00:15:08,200
It's a wonder nothing's gone wrong sooner.

321
00:15:08,200 --> 00:15:09,850
Didn't the director of the HSKP Department

322
00:15:09,850 --> 00:15:11,730
switch to a new laundry vendor?

323
00:15:11,820 --> 00:15:13,360
So why is it still like this?

324
00:15:13,510 --> 00:15:14,950
It's the same.

325
00:15:15,080 --> 00:15:17,240
It still follows Feng's order.

326
00:15:21,200 --> 00:15:23,860
The director of the HSKP Department
named Feng.

327
00:15:24,050 --> 00:15:24,800
Feng Kaixin.

328
00:15:27,210 --> 00:15:29,630
Look, these linens
haven't been replaced for years.

329
00:15:29,630 --> 00:15:31,820
Just bleached white over and over.

330
00:15:31,850 --> 00:15:33,630
How greedy is that?

331
00:15:34,040 --> 00:15:36,160
Treating guests like fools.

332
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:37,720
It's criminal.

333
00:15:38,020 --> 00:15:40,550
Just thinking about it
makes me itch all over.

334
00:15:48,620 --> 00:15:49,580
Everyone,

335
00:15:49,610 --> 00:15:51,010
it's okay to take a break.

336
00:15:51,530 --> 00:15:52,370
Later,

337
00:15:52,860 --> 00:15:55,250
let's hurry up and work harder,

338
00:15:55,280 --> 00:15:56,670
sort these linens out,

339
00:15:56,670 --> 00:15:58,130
and put the new linens on first.

340
00:15:58,130 --> 00:15:58,890
Alright?

341
00:15:59,390 --> 00:16:01,320
I really can't do it anymore, Miyu.

342
00:16:01,570 --> 00:16:03,350
I can't even lift my arms.

343
00:16:03,390 --> 00:16:05,510
These are all clean linens.

344
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:08,070
Who can even tell if we swap them or not?

345
00:16:08,150 --> 00:16:09,150
We might not,

346
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:10,960
but the guests can feel the difference.

347
00:16:10,960 --> 00:16:12,550
Those from the new laundry factory

348
00:16:12,550 --> 00:16:13,870
are still safer.

349
00:16:14,070 --> 00:16:14,940
Ms. Xu,

350
00:16:14,990 --> 00:16:17,230
can you even tell which towel

351
00:16:17,250 --> 00:16:18,680
came from the new laundry

352
00:16:18,700 --> 00:16:20,390
and which from the old?

353
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:21,570
The colors are the same.

354
00:16:21,570 --> 00:16:22,810
They feel the same.

355
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:23,910
What's the difference?

356
00:16:23,910 --> 00:16:26,100
Jia, didn't I just tell you?

357
00:16:26,210 --> 00:16:28,040
We can't just focus
on the surface in service.

358
00:16:28,040 --> 00:16:29,540
Spare us the lectures.

359
00:16:29,560 --> 00:16:31,090
I just want to ask one thing.

360
00:16:31,440 --> 00:16:32,670
This is clearly the higher-ups' fault.

361
00:16:32,670 --> 00:16:34,330
Why do we have to take the fall?

362
00:16:34,590 --> 00:16:35,920
Is it just because we attendants

363
00:16:35,920 --> 00:16:37,630
at the bottom have no voice?

364
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:40,530
We've been working over 10 hours already.

365
00:16:40,870 --> 00:16:43,330
Is this overtime
or some kind of punishment?

366
00:16:43,360 --> 00:16:44,120
I'm sorry.

367
00:16:44,960 --> 00:16:47,270
I didn't think it through.

368
00:16:48,400 --> 00:16:51,350
Everyone, let's push a little longer.

369
00:16:51,590 --> 00:16:53,870
I'll go fight for overtime pay right now.

370
00:17:00,390 --> 00:17:01,450
Overtime pay?

371
00:17:01,560 --> 00:17:03,070
How can you even ask for that?

372
00:17:03,070 --> 00:17:04,710
You caused this huge mess,

373
00:17:03,140 --> 00:17:06,990
[Purong Hotel]

374
00:17:04,730 --> 00:17:06,240
and you still have the nerve
to ask for money?

375
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:07,440
Are you out of your mind?

376
00:17:07,440 --> 00:17:08,200
Mr. Feng,

377
00:17:08,660 --> 00:17:10,720
it's clearly stated
in the employee handbook

378
00:17:10,720 --> 00:17:12,599
that exceeding regular work hours

379
00:17:12,599 --> 00:17:13,790
must be compensated by the hour.

380
00:17:13,790 --> 00:17:15,349
Wh-What compensation?

381
00:17:15,380 --> 00:17:17,099
You drove the guests away.

382
00:17:17,119 --> 00:17:18,740
I should be the one
asking for compensation!

383
00:17:18,740 --> 00:17:20,780
The guests left
because of the linen issue,

384
00:17:20,780 --> 00:17:22,369
not because of us attendants.

385
00:17:22,369 --> 00:17:24,369
How is it not the attendants' fault?

386
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:27,020
It's because you gave them bad service

387
00:17:27,050 --> 00:17:28,990
that they started nitpicking the hardware.

388
00:17:28,990 --> 00:17:30,110
If you had swapped them out more often,

389
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:30,880
how could there

390
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:32,070
have been an allergy issue at all?

391
00:17:32,070 --> 00:17:33,960
The guest's allergic to bleach.

392
00:17:33,960 --> 00:17:36,000
The more often we swap,
the worse the allergy gets.

393
00:17:36,000 --> 00:17:37,070
And regarding the linen issue,

394
00:17:37,070 --> 00:17:38,400
I've been keeping you updated.

395
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,400
Stop right there.

396
00:17:39,420 --> 00:17:40,830
Let me tell you, Xu Miyu,

397
00:17:40,860 --> 00:17:42,100
don't give me that.

398
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:43,750
I made you forewoman.

399
00:17:43,790 --> 00:17:45,780
It's not for you to manage upward on me,

400
00:17:45,780 --> 00:17:48,060
but to manage the people below you

401
00:17:48,090 --> 00:17:49,020
and manage yourself!

402
00:17:49,020 --> 00:17:50,140
What about our overtime pay?

403
00:17:50,140 --> 00:17:51,330
Still on overtime pay, huh?

404
00:17:51,330 --> 00:17:52,480
Do you want to quit?

405
00:17:54,450 --> 00:17:55,550
Anything else?

406
00:17:56,580 --> 00:17:57,380
Nothing.

407
00:18:11,790 --> 00:18:12,620
Everyone.

408
00:18:18,190 --> 00:18:20,280
Let's call it a day.

409
00:18:20,610 --> 00:18:22,300
Go back and rest.

410
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:24,560
Ms. Xu,

411
00:18:25,070 --> 00:18:27,160
did we get our overtime pay?

412
00:18:27,640 --> 00:18:28,990
Clearly no chance.

413
00:18:29,770 --> 00:18:31,770
I knew it. Empty promises as always.

414
00:18:36,570 --> 00:18:38,730
Ms. Xu, I can't take the night shift.

415
00:18:39,480 --> 00:18:40,770
Don't. I'll take it.

416
00:19:05,830 --> 00:19:06,920
Earlier today,

417
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:08,920
the famous Shanghai Purong Hotel

418
00:19:08,920 --> 00:19:10,370
was exposed by self-media

419
00:19:10,370 --> 00:19:12,530
for excessive bleach in its linens,

420
00:19:12,560 --> 00:19:14,310
causing severe allergies to guests.

421
00:19:14,310 --> 00:19:16,830
The incident is currently
under investigation.

422
00:19:16,540 --> 00:19:18,580
[Imperial Court 28, Pujiang]

423
00:19:16,850 --> 00:19:20,250
Relevant departments
may be involved in the investigation.

424
00:19:25,110 --> 00:19:25,920
Hello.

425
00:19:27,610 --> 00:19:28,470
Please come in.

426
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:34,440
This way, please.

427
00:19:50,070 --> 00:19:51,040
Chairman Wei.

428
00:19:52,510 --> 00:19:54,380
I knew you'd come.

429
00:19:54,800 --> 00:19:55,980
If not tonight,

430
00:19:56,170 --> 00:19:57,120
then tomorrow.

431
00:19:58,640 --> 00:19:59,840
Purong Hotel

432
00:20:00,680 --> 00:20:01,550
is currently

433
00:20:01,750 --> 00:20:04,430
facing a critical PR crisis.

434
00:20:05,760 --> 00:20:08,550
I know you won't stand by and do nothing.

435
00:20:08,570 --> 00:20:10,250
It is indeed very difficult

436
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:12,830
to achieve the condition of
turning losses into profits of over 30%

437
00:20:12,830 --> 00:20:13,970
within a year.

438
00:20:13,990 --> 00:20:16,270
But securing Kuanli's investment

439
00:20:16,430 --> 00:20:19,430
is a turning point for Purong.

440
00:20:21,630 --> 00:20:23,260
You don't want to just

441
00:20:23,280 --> 00:20:24,500
give Purong Hotel away.

442
00:20:24,500 --> 00:20:25,790
Purong

443
00:20:25,990 --> 00:20:27,430
can't lose this bet.

444
00:20:27,910 --> 00:20:30,600
I'm prepared to take drastic measures.

445
00:20:32,370 --> 00:20:34,380
Based on my observations recently,

446
00:20:35,190 --> 00:20:37,320
drastic measures might not be enough

447
00:20:37,550 --> 00:20:39,420
for the current Purong Hotel.

448
00:20:40,170 --> 00:20:42,430
We might need to make severe sacrifices.

449
00:20:43,240 --> 00:20:45,940
First, we must reform the system

450
00:20:45,960 --> 00:20:48,960
to change the hotel's mindset
from top to bottom.

451
00:20:48,990 --> 00:20:51,230
Then cut off corrupt collusion.

452
00:20:52,520 --> 00:20:54,920
By rectifying internal corruption,

453
00:20:54,990 --> 00:20:56,510
we must break the profit chains

454
00:20:56,510 --> 00:20:58,410
that severely drain the hotel's wealth.

455
00:20:58,410 --> 00:20:59,820
The first to go

456
00:20:59,850 --> 00:21:01,180
if the HSKP Department.

457
00:21:01,540 --> 00:21:04,100
Beyond the linen issue
making headlines these days,

458
00:21:04,100 --> 00:21:05,970
the toiletries in the HSKP Department

459
00:21:05,970 --> 00:21:07,210
also have

460
00:21:07,380 --> 00:21:09,580
channel and management loopholes.

461
00:21:10,070 --> 00:21:12,730
Of course, these are just
the surface symptoms.

462
00:21:13,550 --> 00:21:14,750
Once the profit chains are cut,

463
00:21:14,750 --> 00:21:17,400
their mutual protection network
will start to crumble.

464
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:19,860
Then we sever the interpersonal collusion.

465
00:21:20,360 --> 00:21:21,380
Corruption is ultimately about

466
00:21:21,380 --> 00:21:24,240
managers stealing from their own posts.

467
00:21:24,320 --> 00:21:26,780
The root of the problem
lies with the people.

468
00:21:27,220 --> 00:21:29,460
If management itself isn't solid,

469
00:21:29,910 --> 00:21:32,110
Purong Hotel's disease can never be cured.

470
00:21:32,110 --> 00:21:33,310
My nephew

471
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:36,700
just doesn't know how to run a hotel.

472
00:21:36,930 --> 00:21:38,460
I invited you here this time

473
00:21:38,480 --> 00:21:40,770
to help him pull up the weeds

474
00:21:40,800 --> 00:21:42,310
and clean up the backyard.

475
00:21:42,580 --> 00:21:45,580
We can't ruin Purong Hotel's reputation.

476
00:21:58,440 --> 00:22:00,150
[Total Attrition Rate]
[Analysis of Attrition Reasons]

477
00:21:58,750 --> 00:22:00,410
The attrition rate is so high.

478
00:22:00,470 --> 00:22:02,640
It's all the reporters
stirring up trouble.

479
00:22:02,640 --> 00:22:04,240
It wasn't a big deal at first,

480
00:22:04,260 --> 00:22:06,340
but some meddlers hyped it up.

481
00:22:07,060 --> 00:22:08,460
Since that's the case,

482
00:22:10,370 --> 00:22:12,770
we might as well
let nature take its course.

483
00:22:13,870 --> 00:22:15,700
Arrange a media briefing

484
00:22:16,040 --> 00:22:17,370
to appease all parties.

485
00:22:18,320 --> 00:22:19,930
That's a good idea.

486
00:22:20,240 --> 00:22:22,730
But we should plan in advance what to say

487
00:22:22,810 --> 00:22:24,540
and how to say it at the meeting.

488
00:22:24,640 --> 00:22:26,370
We can't have any more trouble.

489
00:22:28,290 --> 00:22:29,330
I'm here.

490
00:22:30,670 --> 00:22:32,230
Everything is sorted out.

491
00:22:34,050 --> 00:22:34,910
Zhigang.

492
00:22:39,290 --> 00:22:42,770
Mr. Wei, I've changed
the laundry supplier.

493
00:22:42,930 --> 00:22:44,520
You can trust me to handle things...

494
00:22:44,520 --> 00:22:46,540
What's the use of
changing the laundry supplier?

495
00:22:46,540 --> 00:22:47,670
I told you a long time ago

496
00:22:47,670 --> 00:22:49,560
to focus more on your work.

497
00:22:49,860 --> 00:22:50,810
And what did you do?

498
00:22:50,810 --> 00:22:53,290
All you know is drinking every day.

499
00:22:53,310 --> 00:22:54,560
Now look what you've done,

500
00:22:54,560 --> 00:22:55,770
causing such a huge mess.

501
00:22:55,770 --> 00:22:57,120
How am I supposed to
explain this to the Old Madam,

502
00:22:57,120 --> 00:22:59,030
and to the old folks on the board?

503
00:22:59,050 --> 00:23:00,140
Tell me!

504
00:23:02,070 --> 00:23:02,750
Well,

505
00:23:02,810 --> 00:23:03,700
how about this?

506
00:23:03,730 --> 00:23:06,300
I'll find a few guys
to warn the troublemaker

507
00:23:06,580 --> 00:23:08,640
and make him withdraw the complaint.

508
00:23:09,220 --> 00:23:11,270
You watch too many movies!

509
00:23:11,380 --> 00:23:13,660
Purong Hotel is such a big hotel,

510
00:23:13,690 --> 00:23:15,370
and you want to play gangster?

511
00:23:15,390 --> 00:23:17,450
Alcohol must have ruined your brain.

512
00:23:17,680 --> 00:23:20,480
Kaixin, just drop it.

513
00:23:24,380 --> 00:23:26,660
An allergic reaction
like this has never happened before.

514
00:23:26,610 --> 00:23:28,570
[Home] [Recommend]

515
00:23:27,470 --> 00:23:28,880
At this point,

516
00:23:28,910 --> 00:23:30,500
there's no putting it out.

517
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:33,640
All we can do is steer public opinion

518
00:23:33,640 --> 00:23:36,850
so it doesn't blow back on us.

519
00:23:39,670 --> 00:23:41,130
Shift all the media attention

520
00:23:40,920 --> 00:23:43,160
[Home] [Recommend]

521
00:23:41,350 --> 00:23:43,540
onto her.

522
00:23:43,860 --> 00:23:46,210
After all, she is the one on camera.

523
00:23:46,310 --> 00:23:48,720
And the words came out of her mouth.

524
00:23:48,740 --> 00:23:50,500
We might as well

525
00:23:50,530 --> 00:23:52,560
turn this bleach incident

526
00:23:52,640 --> 00:23:54,400
into her personal behavior.

527
00:23:54,790 --> 00:23:56,900
Like being careless at work

528
00:23:57,040 --> 00:23:58,740
and irresponsible to the guests.

529
00:23:58,740 --> 00:23:59,410
Then,

530
00:23:59,850 --> 00:24:02,400
we will deal with her internally.

531
00:24:02,840 --> 00:24:05,030
Play it down and smooth it over.

532
00:24:06,810 --> 00:24:07,650
Too...

533
00:24:10,800 --> 00:24:12,730
Forewoman of the executive floor?

534
00:24:14,750 --> 00:24:15,980
Just promoted.

535
00:24:16,010 --> 00:24:16,690
Why?

536
00:24:17,020 --> 00:24:18,880
Does she have someone backing her?

537
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:19,620
She...

538
00:24:20,100 --> 00:24:21,430
She works for Old Madam.

539
00:24:23,140 --> 00:24:24,980
You don't know my aunt.

540
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:26,950
She looks kind,

541
00:24:27,220 --> 00:24:29,370
but she is an absolute businesswoman.

542
00:24:29,710 --> 00:24:30,910
She is very ruthless.

543
00:24:31,420 --> 00:24:33,340
The trouble is at her doorstep now.

544
00:24:33,340 --> 00:24:35,610
As long as you handle this matter well,

545
00:24:35,700 --> 00:24:37,490
she won't say anything about it.

546
00:24:37,490 --> 00:24:37,950
[Monday, January 6th,
7th of the 12th Lunar Month]

547
00:24:44,530 --> 00:24:46,460
Ji Feng went to see the chairwoman.

548
00:24:51,440 --> 00:24:53,890
It's just that you took
on this role in a crisis

549
00:24:53,890 --> 00:24:55,970
without even a proper ceremony.

550
00:24:56,710 --> 00:24:58,110
You flatter me, Ms. Wei.

551
00:24:59,120 --> 00:25:00,790
It's my honor

552
00:25:00,820 --> 00:25:02,610
to help Purong Hotel

553
00:25:02,640 --> 00:25:04,130
at such a critical moment.

554
00:25:04,160 --> 00:25:06,490
Your current achievements and abilities

555
00:25:06,810 --> 00:25:09,960
prove that I wasn't wrong about you.

556
00:25:10,350 --> 00:25:13,030
Being able to repay your kindness
in recognizing my talent

557
00:25:13,030 --> 00:25:15,350
is my opportunity and glory.

558
00:25:15,370 --> 00:25:19,240
Do you need me to escort you
to your new post tomorrow?

559
00:25:20,610 --> 00:25:22,600
The hotel is currently
at the center of public opinion.

560
00:25:22,600 --> 00:25:25,930
If you go, you'll just give
the reporters more to talk about.

561
00:25:26,780 --> 00:25:29,180
It's better if you direct things remotely.

562
00:25:31,940 --> 00:25:33,480
The time for the press conference is set.

563
00:25:33,480 --> 00:25:34,430
9 a.m. tomorrow.

564
00:25:34,460 --> 00:25:36,930
I'll personally oversee the venue setup.

565
00:25:37,350 --> 00:25:38,620
As for the Communications Department,

566
00:25:38,620 --> 00:25:40,640
I told them to draft
a press release first,

567
00:25:40,640 --> 00:25:42,560
find some influencers to post it,

568
00:25:42,850 --> 00:25:44,280
and stir up some buzz.

569
00:25:46,260 --> 00:25:47,750
[Aunt]

570
00:26:03,440 --> 00:26:04,070
Aunt.

571
00:26:04,100 --> 00:26:04,870
Siyuan.

572
00:26:05,170 --> 00:26:08,250
A new general manager
will take office tomorrow,

573
00:26:08,310 --> 00:26:09,790
to deal with this crisis.

574
00:26:10,050 --> 00:26:11,960
I invited him back from abroad.

575
00:26:12,270 --> 00:26:14,030
He is very experienced.

576
00:26:14,410 --> 00:26:15,540
You should know him.

577
00:26:15,550 --> 00:26:16,640
His name is Ji Feng.

578
00:26:17,240 --> 00:26:18,920
Do you remember him?

579
00:26:21,690 --> 00:26:24,750
[Ten years ago]

580
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:23,920
Aunt,

581
00:26:23,950 --> 00:26:25,030
why?

582
00:26:27,320 --> 00:26:29,320
You promised me.

583
00:26:29,440 --> 00:26:32,110
You said you'd give me
the recommendation letter.

584
00:26:32,110 --> 00:26:34,200
Why did you go back on your word
and give it to someone else?

585
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:34,960
What I told you

586
00:26:34,960 --> 00:26:36,490
was that I would think about it.

587
00:26:36,490 --> 00:26:38,450
I was almost on my knees.

588
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:40,070
What else do you want me to do?

589
00:26:40,070 --> 00:26:41,310
Some nobody foreman

590
00:26:41,310 --> 00:26:42,710
just shows up out of nowhere

591
00:26:42,710 --> 00:26:44,230
and takes what's mine?

592
00:26:44,260 --> 00:26:45,530
Why is that, Aunt?

593
00:26:45,710 --> 00:26:46,880
You'd rather support someone

594
00:26:46,880 --> 00:26:48,680
who has nothing to do with you

595
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:51,240
than help your own nephew!

596
00:26:52,290 --> 00:26:53,380
Wei Siyuan!

597
00:26:53,790 --> 00:26:54,790
Over the years,

598
00:26:54,810 --> 00:26:56,640
I have been carefully cultivating

599
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:58,310
useful talents.

600
00:26:58,380 --> 00:27:00,900
Ji Feng is capable and ambitious.

601
00:27:00,990 --> 00:27:03,790
He came to me himself
for a recommendation letter.

602
00:27:03,930 --> 00:27:05,900
Of course I am willing to build

603
00:27:05,930 --> 00:27:07,390
this good relationship for Purong.

604
00:27:07,390 --> 00:27:09,500
Then why couldn't that person be me?

605
00:27:09,530 --> 00:27:11,470
Am I that useless to you?

606
00:27:11,590 --> 00:27:14,900
Do you really want
to learn something by going abroad?

607
00:27:14,930 --> 00:27:17,410
You fool around outside all day.

608
00:27:17,430 --> 00:27:19,970
How can I feel at ease
letting you go abroad?

609
00:27:21,680 --> 00:27:23,830
Hello, Siyuan?

610
00:27:25,380 --> 00:27:26,180
Aunt.

611
00:27:26,730 --> 00:27:28,450
Okay, I got it.

612
00:27:50,900 --> 00:27:52,510
Welcome, friends from the media.

613
00:27:52,510 --> 00:27:54,350
Please get your press badges first,

614
00:27:54,350 --> 00:27:55,590
then ahead,

615
00:27:55,590 --> 00:27:57,030
you will see our sign-in area.

616
00:27:57,030 --> 00:27:58,190
Just sign in there.

617
00:27:58,220 --> 00:27:59,160
If you need anything,

618
00:27:59,160 --> 00:28:00,160
you can come to me anytime.

619
00:28:00,160 --> 00:28:01,590
Yes, get your press badges here.

620
00:28:01,590 --> 00:28:02,350
Thank you.

621
00:28:01,630 --> 00:28:06,800
[Purong Hotel Cloth Safety
Media Exchange Meeting]

622
00:28:09,040 --> 00:28:12,070
[Purong Hotel Cloth Safety
Media Exchange Meeting]

623
00:28:14,070 --> 00:28:15,790
Hello, hello, hello.

624
00:28:15,470 --> 00:28:18,040
[Sign-in Desk]

625
00:28:18,520 --> 00:28:20,520
[Purong Hotel Cloth Safety
Media Exchange Meeting]

626
00:28:20,550 --> 00:28:21,830
[Sign-in Desk]

627
00:28:24,440 --> 00:28:26,130
Hello, everyone.

628
00:28:26,160 --> 00:28:28,480
Welcome to today's program.

629
00:28:26,630 --> 00:28:29,050
[Boyuan TV]

630
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:30,740
Right now, I am inside the Purong Hotel.

631
00:28:30,760 --> 00:28:31,640
As you can see,

632
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:33,310
we're at the sign-in desk

633
00:28:33,310 --> 00:28:36,040
for Purong Hotel's
linen safety media briefing.

634
00:28:40,670 --> 00:28:41,840
[Tuesday, January 7th,
8th Day of the 12th Lunar Month]

635
00:28:50,540 --> 00:28:51,640
[Welcome to Purong Hotel]

636
00:29:18,780 --> 00:29:19,540
Mr. Wei.

637
00:29:19,950 --> 00:29:21,780
The press conference is about to begin.

638
00:29:21,780 --> 00:29:22,780
As for the speech,

639
00:29:23,000 --> 00:29:25,260
are you sure you don't need one prepared?

640
00:29:26,400 --> 00:29:27,530
No need.

641
00:29:27,720 --> 00:29:28,660
I know what to say.

642
00:29:28,660 --> 00:29:29,460
Okay.

643
00:29:30,010 --> 00:29:31,570
I'll go keep an eye on the venue.

644
00:29:31,570 --> 00:29:34,060
[Purong Hotel]

645
00:29:35,170 --> 00:29:36,670
[General Manager's Office]

646
00:29:42,300 --> 00:29:46,400
[General Manager's Office]

647
00:29:43,310 --> 00:29:45,060
Ji Feng? You're here.

648
00:29:45,200 --> 00:29:45,850
Come.

649
00:29:46,550 --> 00:29:47,750
Please, have a seat.

650
00:29:53,520 --> 00:29:55,020
You came just in time.

651
00:29:55,100 --> 00:29:57,100
I got a call from Aunt last night.

652
00:29:57,130 --> 00:29:58,750
You have no idea—it felt like

653
00:29:58,930 --> 00:30:01,260
a huge weight was lifted off my shoulders.

654
00:30:02,870 --> 00:30:04,280
It was such a relief.

655
00:30:07,370 --> 00:30:08,160
Ji Feng.

656
00:30:08,590 --> 00:30:09,960
We were in a hurry last time we met,

657
00:30:09,960 --> 00:30:12,240
and there were things I didn't get to say.

658
00:30:13,290 --> 00:30:14,570
In the past,

659
00:30:14,600 --> 00:30:16,670
we had some misunderstandings.

660
00:30:17,240 --> 00:30:19,750
Let this cup of tea be my apology to you.

661
00:30:20,030 --> 00:30:22,110
I hope you can let bygones be bygones

662
00:30:22,230 --> 00:30:23,160
and help Purong.

663
00:30:25,040 --> 00:30:26,570
Mr. Wei, you're too polite.

664
00:30:27,500 --> 00:30:29,740
I've long forgotten about the past.

665
00:30:29,980 --> 00:30:32,570
I came back to learn from my seniors.

666
00:30:32,750 --> 00:30:34,120
What seniors?

667
00:30:34,140 --> 00:30:36,490
How can I compare to returnees like you?

668
00:30:37,120 --> 00:30:38,550
What happened these past few days

669
00:30:38,550 --> 00:30:39,610
is a real headache.

670
00:30:39,750 --> 00:30:40,960
My subordinates and I

671
00:30:41,070 --> 00:30:42,330
can't manage it at all.

672
00:30:43,250 --> 00:30:46,100
Then how do you plan
to deal with it, Mr. Wei?

673
00:30:46,130 --> 00:30:47,200
We...

674
00:30:48,150 --> 00:30:48,940
Come in.

675
00:30:51,580 --> 00:30:54,280
Mr. Wei, the press conference is ready.

676
00:30:54,310 --> 00:30:55,710
Okay, I got it. You can go.

677
00:30:58,150 --> 00:31:00,150
Did I come at a bad time?

678
00:31:00,170 --> 00:31:01,170
Not at all.

679
00:31:02,520 --> 00:31:03,960
You came at the perfect time.

680
00:31:03,960 --> 00:31:05,480
How about we walk together

681
00:31:05,510 --> 00:31:06,790
and talk on the way?

682
00:31:06,830 --> 00:31:07,310
Okay.

683
00:31:07,330 --> 00:31:08,130
Come on.

684
00:31:13,040 --> 00:31:13,380
After you.

685
00:31:13,380 --> 00:31:13,980
After you.

686
00:31:14,210 --> 00:31:14,940
Please.

687
00:31:17,650 --> 00:31:19,590
This press conference
is making such a big scene.

688
00:31:19,590 --> 00:31:21,540
Everyone from the grassroots
to the leaders has to attend.

689
00:31:21,540 --> 00:31:22,850
What exactly is going on?

690
00:31:22,850 --> 00:31:23,610
I don't know.

691
00:31:23,640 --> 00:31:24,900
Mr. Qian spent the whole day yesterday

692
00:31:24,900 --> 00:31:26,250
in Mr. Wei's office.

693
00:31:26,430 --> 00:31:27,170
I guess the matter

694
00:31:27,170 --> 00:31:28,000
is not small.

695
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:30,290
Why do you care if it's big or small?

696
00:31:30,290 --> 00:31:31,820
It's not our place to worry.

697
00:31:32,810 --> 00:31:34,740
Just go in and listen.

698
00:31:34,600 --> 00:31:37,220
[Purong Hotel Cloth Safety
Media Exchange Meeting]

699
00:31:34,850 --> 00:31:36,380
Let's take our seats first.

700
00:31:38,830 --> 00:31:39,550
Mr. Wei.

701
00:31:40,900 --> 00:31:41,900
Mr. Ji?

702
00:31:44,010 --> 00:31:45,590
Mr. Ji helped rescue

703
00:31:45,590 --> 00:31:47,950
a heart attack patient
on the executive floor.

704
00:31:47,950 --> 00:31:48,710
Really?

705
00:31:49,340 --> 00:31:50,010
Mr. Wei.

706
00:31:50,340 --> 00:31:51,330
The media is here.

707
00:31:51,330 --> 00:31:52,880
The reporters from Weekend Times
are also here,

708
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:56,080
and they want to arrange
an exclusive interview with you.

709
00:31:56,290 --> 00:31:57,170
Ji Feng.

710
00:31:57,440 --> 00:31:58,930
I forgot my phone.

711
00:31:59,050 --> 00:31:59,910
How about this?

712
00:32:00,230 --> 00:32:01,450
You take Mr. Ji over there first

713
00:32:01,450 --> 00:32:02,850
and let him sit in my seat.

714
00:32:04,830 --> 00:32:06,220
Is that appropriate?

715
00:32:06,250 --> 00:32:08,120
That's the general manager's seat.

716
00:32:08,120 --> 00:32:10,000
Mr. Ji is the future general manager
of our hotel.

717
00:32:10,000 --> 00:32:11,800
You still think it's inappropriate?

718
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:13,330
Don't just stand there, go.

719
00:32:14,060 --> 00:32:14,790
Understood.

720
00:32:14,960 --> 00:32:16,360
Mr. Ji, please follow me.

721
00:32:16,360 --> 00:32:16,800
Okay.

722
00:32:16,820 --> 00:32:18,020
I'll be there in a bit.

723
00:32:27,800 --> 00:32:28,600
This way.

724
00:32:35,160 --> 00:32:36,160
This way, please.

725
00:32:39,430 --> 00:32:41,160
What's he doing sitting there?

726
00:32:46,480 --> 00:32:49,640
Purong Hotel's media meeting
is about to begin.

727
00:32:49,640 --> 00:32:52,300
Friends from the press,
please take your seats.

728
00:32:54,050 --> 00:32:55,310
Here to watch the show?

729
00:32:57,290 --> 00:32:58,570
You got a good seat.

730
00:32:59,250 --> 00:33:00,390
Why are you here?

731
00:33:00,640 --> 00:33:03,420
I am the future chairman
of Purong Hotel.

732
00:33:03,480 --> 00:33:06,410
How could I not come
when something this big happens?

733
00:33:06,710 --> 00:33:09,230
Respected leaders, guests,

734
00:33:09,250 --> 00:33:11,010
and friends from the media,

735
00:33:11,040 --> 00:33:12,210
good morning.

736
00:33:12,310 --> 00:33:14,570
It's a great honor
to have this opportunity

737
00:33:14,570 --> 00:33:15,400
to gather with you all

738
00:33:15,400 --> 00:33:18,030
at Purong Hotel's media exchange meeting.

739
00:33:18,240 --> 00:33:19,250
Today,

740
00:33:19,350 --> 00:33:20,030
we will

741
00:33:20,030 --> 00:33:21,920
give a sincere response

742
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:23,030
regarding the bleach incident

743
00:33:23,030 --> 00:33:25,400
at Purong Hotel a few days ago.

744
00:33:25,420 --> 00:33:26,870
A sincere response?

745
00:33:27,330 --> 00:33:29,310
That old fox Wei Siyuan is absent again.

746
00:33:29,310 --> 00:33:31,420
I wonder which fearless person

747
00:33:31,440 --> 00:33:33,400
will be brought out to do
the damage control this time.

748
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:35,160
Now, let's welcome

749
00:33:35,290 --> 00:33:37,550
the new general manager of Purong Hotel,

750
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:40,000
Mr. Ji Feng, to answer your questions.

751
00:33:41,520 --> 00:33:42,780
Who is Ji Feng?

752
00:33:43,680 --> 00:33:45,180
When did our hotel get
a new general manager?

753
00:33:45,180 --> 00:33:46,250
Yeah.

754
00:33:47,660 --> 00:33:48,590
Mr. Ji.

755
00:33:49,430 --> 00:33:50,120
Please.

756
00:34:23,190 --> 00:34:24,710
Good morning, everyone.

757
00:34:25,050 --> 00:34:27,650
I'm the new general manager
of Purong Hotel,

758
00:34:28,050 --> 00:34:29,080
Ji Feng.

759
00:34:32,120 --> 00:34:34,040
I'll keep this brief.

760
00:34:34,170 --> 00:34:35,460
Regarding the incident

761
00:34:35,460 --> 00:34:37,320
where excess bleach in the linens

762
00:34:37,370 --> 00:34:38,620
of the HSKP Department

763
00:34:38,620 --> 00:34:40,679
caused skin allergies in our guests,

764
00:34:41,010 --> 00:34:43,340
after investigations by various parties,

765
00:34:43,340 --> 00:34:46,870
it has been determined to be
a major internal error of the hotel.

766
00:34:50,370 --> 00:34:53,429
Purong Hotel will
take full responsibility.

767
00:34:53,460 --> 00:34:54,580
Please rest assured.

768
00:34:54,580 --> 00:34:56,060
Bring Xu Miyu here.

769
00:34:56,380 --> 00:34:57,320
Hurry up.

770
00:34:58,400 --> 00:35:00,080
Why did the new
general manager admit to it?

771
00:35:00,080 --> 00:35:01,570
What is he trying to do?

772
00:35:07,150 --> 00:35:08,030
Ms. Xu.

773
00:35:08,970 --> 00:35:09,740
Mr. Wu.

774
00:35:09,770 --> 00:35:11,170
Come with me for a moment.

775
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:13,470
What is it?

776
00:35:14,590 --> 00:35:15,550
I'm sorry

777
00:35:15,990 --> 00:35:17,880
to meet you for the first time
in this way today.

778
00:35:17,070 --> 00:35:20,620
[Purong Hotel Cloth Safety
Media Exchange Meeting]

779
00:35:18,190 --> 00:35:19,960
Regarding Purong's
internal issues this time,

780
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:21,490
I will never tolerate them.

781
00:35:21,740 --> 00:35:22,660
Here,

782
00:35:23,470 --> 00:35:24,670
I promise to all of you

783
00:35:25,000 --> 00:35:28,120
and the consumers in front of the camera

784
00:35:28,150 --> 00:35:29,100
Purong Hotel

785
00:35:29,170 --> 00:35:30,460
will definitely replace

786
00:35:30,460 --> 00:35:32,360
the problematic linen as soon as possible,

787
00:35:32,360 --> 00:35:34,340
thoroughly investigate
the cause of the accident,

788
00:35:34,340 --> 00:35:35,560
and welcome everyone's stay

789
00:35:35,560 --> 00:35:38,420
with a brand new look
in the shortest possible time.

790
00:35:40,390 --> 00:35:41,160
Go in.

791
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:44,620
It's her.

792
00:35:44,640 --> 00:35:46,190
She is the person in the video.

793
00:35:46,190 --> 00:35:47,400
That's her.

794
00:35:47,400 --> 00:35:48,230
Yes, it's her.

795
00:35:48,230 --> 00:35:49,490
She's that attendant.

796
00:35:50,030 --> 00:35:51,760
Hello, hello.

797
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:52,760
Hello.

798
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:54,150
Excuse me.

799
00:35:54,150 --> 00:35:55,400
Did you run any tests

800
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:56,360
before claiming there was no problem...

801
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:58,840
-with the towels?
- What was the situation when the guest fell ill?

802
00:35:58,840 --> 00:35:59,920
Do you ever feel any guilt

803
00:35:59,920 --> 00:36:00,880
when you brushed off the guests?

804
00:36:00,880 --> 00:36:01,800
What's your relationship with

805
00:36:01,800 --> 00:36:02,760
the linen service company?

806
00:36:02,760 --> 00:36:04,760
-Did you profit from it?
-Who asked you to do this?

807
00:36:04,760 --> 00:36:05,920
Did someone else support you?

808
00:36:05,920 --> 00:36:07,480
Did the hotel support you?

809
00:36:07,480 --> 00:36:08,340
Please tell us.

810
00:36:21,060 --> 00:36:22,080
Miss.

811
00:36:22,510 --> 00:36:24,710
You don't have to answer any questions.

812
00:36:28,850 --> 00:36:30,570
[Purong Hotel Cloth Safety
Media Exchange Meeting]

813
00:36:43,440 --> 00:36:44,770
Friends from the media,

814
00:36:45,550 --> 00:36:47,960
I'm the only spokesperson
appointed by Purong Hotel

815
00:36:47,960 --> 00:36:49,480
regarding this incident.

816
00:36:49,690 --> 00:36:50,870
I will answer

817
00:36:50,900 --> 00:36:52,820
all your questions.

818
00:36:53,670 --> 00:36:55,490
Please return to your seats. Thank you.

819
00:36:55,490 --> 00:36:56,820
Thank you for your time.

820
00:37:14,760 --> 00:37:15,800
Excessive bleach

821
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:18,030
is essentially not a service issue,

822
00:37:18,200 --> 00:37:21,110
but an oversight in executive management.

823
00:37:23,700 --> 00:37:25,710
As for how we will handle this matter,

824
00:37:25,710 --> 00:37:27,290
within 48 hours,

825
00:37:27,360 --> 00:37:28,940
I will give you a proper answer.

826
00:37:28,940 --> 00:37:30,230
Mr. Ji, may I ask

827
00:37:30,290 --> 00:37:31,510
if the excessive use of bleach

828
00:37:31,510 --> 00:37:33,510
is already a tacitly accepted fact

829
00:37:33,510 --> 00:37:34,760
within Purong Hotel?

830
00:37:35,360 --> 00:37:38,290
How long has this been
tacitly accepted internally?

831
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,550
That is a very good question.

832
00:37:40,550 --> 00:37:41,980
What you're asking is exactly

833
00:37:41,980 --> 00:37:43,640
what we'll investigate next.

834
00:38:06,670 --> 00:38:08,630
Well played, Mr. Ji.

835
00:38:09,260 --> 00:38:10,550
You kept it from me for so long.

836
00:38:10,550 --> 00:38:12,300
You clearly didn't see me as a friend.

837
00:38:12,300 --> 00:38:13,920
You misunderstood, Mr. Duan.

838
00:38:13,920 --> 00:38:14,840
It was an emergency.

839
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:17,070
I was forced into it.

840
00:38:17,240 --> 00:38:18,550
You saw it just now.

841
00:38:18,630 --> 00:38:20,000
I had no choice.

842
00:38:21,110 --> 00:38:23,440
I offered you an olive branch,
but you refused.

843
00:38:23,440 --> 00:38:25,440
And now you're standing against me.

844
00:38:25,440 --> 00:38:27,060
Whatever Wei Wanjun is paying you,

845
00:38:27,060 --> 00:38:28,430
I'll double it.

846
00:38:29,810 --> 00:38:31,980
I'm flattered you think
so highly of me, Mr. Duan.

847
00:38:31,980 --> 00:38:34,550
Then all the more reason
for me to prove myself first

848
00:38:34,550 --> 00:38:37,320
before I discuss my worth with you.

849
00:38:39,690 --> 00:38:40,520
Thanks.

850
00:38:50,550 --> 00:38:53,550
You just want to beat me.

851
00:38:54,910 --> 00:38:55,870
In your dreams.

852
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:05,710
Ji Feng.

853
00:39:07,360 --> 00:39:09,180
I should address you
as General Manager now.

854
00:39:09,180 --> 00:39:10,570
Why are you standing here?

855
00:39:10,570 --> 00:39:11,540
I...

856
00:39:11,850 --> 00:39:12,830
I forgot to tell you,

857
00:39:12,830 --> 00:39:14,580
I vacated my office for you.

858
00:39:14,610 --> 00:39:15,490
Wait a moment.

859
00:39:15,710 --> 00:39:16,710
Wu.

860
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:18,430
Mr. Wei.

861
00:39:18,450 --> 00:39:19,930
Mr. Ji is here.
Get the keys and open the door.

862
00:39:19,930 --> 00:39:20,680
Okay.

863
00:39:24,220 --> 00:39:25,090
Mr. Ji,

864
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:28,040
you're the person Purong Hotel

865
00:39:28,060 --> 00:39:29,260
needs most right now.

866
00:39:29,760 --> 00:39:31,620
To be honest, I thought this would

867
00:39:31,840 --> 00:39:33,310
take a long time, but you're

868
00:39:33,310 --> 00:39:34,980
planning to move fast.

869
00:39:35,100 --> 00:39:37,510
Solving such a thorny crisis in 48 hours,

870
00:39:37,530 --> 00:39:39,300
it's like a miracle.

871
00:39:39,640 --> 00:39:41,280
We're all waiting to see.

872
00:39:41,300 --> 00:39:42,830
Do you have any ideas, Mr. Wei?

873
00:39:42,830 --> 00:39:44,570
What ideas could I have?

874
00:39:44,950 --> 00:39:46,790
I'm completely overwhelmed.

875
00:39:46,850 --> 00:39:47,890
It's a huge mess.

876
00:39:47,920 --> 00:39:49,780
My brain isn't working properly.

877
00:39:49,840 --> 00:39:50,670
But look,

878
00:39:50,350 --> 00:39:52,070
[General Manager's Office]

879
00:39:50,670 --> 00:39:52,360
whatever resources you need,

880
00:39:52,670 --> 00:39:53,480
feel free to use them.

881
00:39:53,480 --> 00:39:53,860
Okay.

882
00:39:54,030 --> 00:39:54,710
Also,

883
00:39:54,930 --> 00:39:56,580
I'm your soldier now.

884
00:39:56,670 --> 00:39:58,330
I'm at your disposal anytime.

885
00:39:59,440 --> 00:40:00,400
Mr. Ji, please.

886
00:40:01,690 --> 00:40:03,150
Mr. Wei, this is...

887
00:40:04,090 --> 00:40:04,940
Secretary Wu.

888
00:40:05,440 --> 00:40:06,760
From now on, he's your secretary.

889
00:40:06,760 --> 00:40:07,440
Feel free to use him.

890
00:40:07,440 --> 00:40:07,960
Okay.

891
00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:11,030
Then please inform everyone, Secretary Wu,

892
00:40:11,030 --> 00:40:14,360
that there will be a full
management team meeting in an hour.

893
00:40:15,760 --> 00:40:17,160
Why are you looking at me?

894
00:40:17,320 --> 00:40:19,320
Mr. Ji told you to inform them, so go.

895
00:40:20,590 --> 00:40:21,710
Okay, Mr. Ji.

896
00:40:27,150 --> 00:40:28,350
Thank you for your support, Mr. Wei.

897
00:40:28,220 --> 00:40:30,250
[General Manager's Office]

898
00:40:28,550 --> 00:40:29,990
Of course.

899
00:40:30,660 --> 00:40:32,950
Do you want me to show you around?

900
00:40:36,110 --> 00:40:36,630
No need.

901
00:40:37,070 --> 00:40:38,790
I'll go change.

902
00:40:38,830 --> 00:40:39,630
See you later

903
00:40:39,660 --> 00:40:40,790
in the meeting room.

904
00:40:41,280 --> 00:40:42,150
Okay.

905
00:40:46,780 --> 00:40:52,650
[General Manager's Office]

906
00:40:47,650 --> 00:40:48,810
Ungrateful.

